subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
Customs, Etiquette and Manners
lead_paragraph: There are 90 suites at Arthur Ashe Stadium, and a shocking number of the people who populate those areas have shown little interest in the matches, but plenty of interest in having a grand old time.
